headline: How Prologis’s (PLD) EV Charging Network Deal Could Reshape Its Logistics Infrastructure Strategy
summary: EV Realty and Prologis Mobility recently announced a partnership to link their electric vehicle charging sites across major freight corridors in Northern and Southern California, aiming to streamline charging access for commercial fleets at key logistics hubs. This collaboration addresses one of the main roadblocks for commercial EV adoption by simplifying network access, and highlights Prologis's push into value-added sustainable infrastructure services.
